-----
LiteCommerce software requires license certificate file to run. License certific
ate is a text file with digital signature which confirms your rights for the lic
ense. Please download your license certificate from LiteCommerce members area ww
w.litecommerce.com/wmembers.php where you downloaded this copy of LiteCommerce s
oftware. Then paste license certificate in the text area below.

There are two types of certificates available: commercial license certificate an
d development license certificate.
Commercial certificate should be used live environment. With commercial certific
ate you store work without any limitations.
Development certificate can be used for non commercial purposes only (eg. when d
eveloping your online store on your office or home computer). With development l
icense the software periodically displays warning that this copy of the software
 is for development purposes only. Development certificate expires in 2 months b
 ut can be renewed at any time free of charge.

 Hint: If you misspelled your license URL when purchasing the software you can do
 wnload and install development certificate while receiving updated commercial li
 cense certificate.
 te.
